## üö® CRITICAL REQUIREMENT: SHADCN/UI COMPONENTS ONLY üö®

**ABSOLUTE RULE**: This project uses shadcn/ui for **ALL** UI elements. 

### ‚ùå PROHIBITED:
- **NEVER** create custom UI components (buttons, inputs, cards, dialogs, etc.)
- **NEVER** use other UI libraries (Material-UI, Ant Design, Chakra UI, etc.)
- **NEVER** build UI components from scratch using only Tailwind classes
- **NEVER** create custom styled components for UI elements

### ‚úÖ REQUIRED:
- **ALWAYS** use shadcn/ui components for ALL UI needs
- **ALWAYS** check if a shadcn/ui component exists before implementing UI
- **ALWAYS** install missing shadcn/ui components using `npx shadcn@latest add <component>`
- **ALWAYS** extend/customize shadcn/ui components if modifications are needed

### üìã The ONLY Exceptions:
